<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0595137a-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s2024"><num value="2024">§ 2024.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary from time to time to carry out the provisions of this subchapter, which sums are authorized to be appropriated to remain available until expended.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0595137b-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/283/tIII/s304">Pub. L. 89–283, title III, § 304</ref>, <date date="1965-10-21">Oct. 21, 1965</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/79/1021">79 Stat. 1021</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
